</li>
<li id="cite_note-Harris2015-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_18-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_18-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHarrisBringhurst2015" class="citation book cs1">Harris, Matthew L.; <a href="/wiki/Newell_G._Bringhurst" title="Newell G. Bringhurst">Bringhurst, Newell G.</a> (2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Pn20CgAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PAiii"><i>The Mormon Church and Blacks: A Documentary History</i></a>. Chicago: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780252081217" title="Special:BookSources/9780252081217"><bdi>9780252081217</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mormon+Church+and+Blacks%3A+A+Documentary+History&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Illinois+Press&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=9780252081217&amp;rft.aulast=Harris&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew+L.&amp;rft.au=Bringhurst%2C+Newell+G.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DPn20CgAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPAiii&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AExaltation+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
