<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMcCombs2017" class="citation news cs1">McCombs, Brady (December 21, 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://apnews.com/article/992dd887f7b948d0a08055dff0363aa4">"Mormon baptisms of Holocaust victims draw ire"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Associated_Press_News" class="mw-redirect" title="Associated Press News">Associated Press News</a></i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Associated+Press+News&amp;rft.atitle=Mormon+baptisms+of+Holocaust+victims+draw+ire&amp;rft.date=2017-12-21&amp;rft.aulast=McCombs&amp;rft.aufirst=Brady&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2F992dd887f7b948d0a08055dff0363aa4&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AExaltation+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
