<li id="cite_note-Eternal-41"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Eternal_41-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFRicks" class="citation book cs1">Ricks, Shirley S. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/digital/collection/EoM/id/5716">"Eternal Lives, Eternal Increase"</a>. In Ludlow, Daniel H. (ed.). <i><a href="/wiki/Encyclopedia_of_Mormonism" title="Encyclopedia of Mormonism">Encyclopedia of Mormonism</a></i>. New York City: <a href="/wiki/Macmillan_Publishers" title="Macmillan Publishers">Macmillan Publishers</a>. p.&#160;465. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-02-904040-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-02-904040-9"><bdi>978-0-02-904040-9</bdi></a>. <q>A husband and wife who are married<span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>[...] are promised they shall inherit 'thrones, kingdoms<span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>[...] and a continuation of the seeds forever and ever.'<span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>[...] They share in the promises of eternal posterity made to Abraham and Sarah<span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>[...] '[that they should] continue as innumerable as the stars'<span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>[...] and enjoy a continuation of seeds forever, or eternal increase.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Eternal+Lives%2C+Eternal+Increase&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclopedia+of+Mormonism&amp;rft.place=New+York+City&amp;rft.pages=465&amp;rft.pub=Macmillan+Publishers&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-02-904040-9&amp;rft.aulast=Ricks&amp;rft.aufirst=Shirley+S.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fcontentdm.lib.byu.edu%2Fdigital%2Fcollection%2FEoM%2Fid%2F5716&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AExaltation+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-42"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-42">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation book cs1">"Alma 39–42: The Great Plan of Happiness". <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/come-follow-me-for-sunday-school-book-of-mormon-2020/30?lang=eng"><i>Come, Follow Me—For Sunday School: Book of Mormon 2020</i></a>. Salt Lake City: <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>. 2020. <q>Worldly sex becomes a total obsession because it never fulfills its promises. God-ordained marital intimacy is glorious and will continue eternally for covenant-keeping husbands and wives.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Alma+39%E2%80%9342%3A+The+Great+Plan+of+Happiness&amp;rft.btitle=Come%2C+Follow+Me%E2%80%94For+Sunday+School%3A+Book+of+Mormon+2020&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=2020&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fmanual%2Fcome-follow-me-for-sunday-school-book-of-mormon-2020%2F30%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AExaltation+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWatson_Nelson2017" class="citation web cs1"><a href="/wiki/Wendy_Watson_Nelson" title="Wendy Watson Nelson">Watson Nelson, Wendy</a> (January 8, 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/broadcasts/article/worldwide-devotionals/2017/01/love-and-marriage?lang=eng">"Love and Marriage"</a>. <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Love+and+Marriage&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=2017-01-08&amp;rft.aulast=Watson+Nelson&amp;rft.aufirst=Wendy&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fbroadcasts%2Farticle%2Fworldwide-devotionals%2F2017%2F01%2Flove-and-marriage%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AExaltation+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
